        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>For the babes who style before makeup or want their blowout kink-free! Our puffy headband will keep your hair off your face while you prep for a night out (or in!). Soft on roots, it won’t mess up your look – and it's so cute, you'll wanna wear it out. </p>",
