            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QnkEdx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does it work?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We recommend using the mask <strong>1-2 times per week</strong> for best results.<strong><br/><br/>1️⃣  Prep</strong> – Cleanse your face & apply toner or serum.<br/><br/><strong>2️⃣  Apply</strong> – Remove the mask from the pouch & peel off the protective films.<br/><br/><strong>3️⃣  Wear</strong> – Place it on your face & leave for 1-2 hours (or until transparent).<br/><br/><strong>4️⃣  Remove</strong> – Gently take off the mask & pat in the extra essence.<br/><br/><strong>5️⃣  Glow</strong> – Enjoy hydrated, plump, and radiant skin!</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it for sensitive skin?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes! Designed to be gentle on the skin. Our mask does not strip moisture or dry out, making it ideal for all skin types.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_kwzWVt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We do not include any harmful parabens or other nasties. We also NEVER test on animals.</p><ul><li><strong>Collagen (25%)</strong><br/>Known for its brightening power, this multitasking vitamin refines pores, evens tone, and boosts skin clarity.<br/></li><li><strong>Niacinamide (25%)</strong> – Known for its brightening power, this multitasking vitamin refines pores, evens tone, and boosts skin clarity.<br/></li><li><strong>Hyaluronic Acid (20%)</strong> – A hydration powerhouse that deeply moisturizes and helps retain water for plump, dewy skin.<br/></li><li><strong>Vitamin E (Tocopherol, 20%)</strong> – A soothing antioxidant that protects the skin barrier and reduces visible signs of stress and aging.<br/></li><li><strong>Glycerin (10%)</strong> – A natural humectant that draws moisture into the skin, keeping it soft, supple, and nourished all day.<br/></li></ul><p>As with all skincare products, we highly recommend & urge you please patch test the mask serum on the skin of the arm or hand before using fully as some people are more sensitive than others or have allergic reactions to blends of ingredients.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Delivery",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed, please allow 24 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time:</strong><br/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-8 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information:</strong><br/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
